OL,3,CBarber jailed after attacking man with
OL,4,Cscissors
OL,6,FA barber who attacked a man with
OL,7,Fscissors in Brighton has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor five years.
OL,10,FAdam Pirot from Roedean Road was
OL,11,Fworking in a barbershop on Preston
OL,12,FStreet when he launched an attack over
OL,13,Fa disagreement.
OL,15,FHe followed the man out of the shop
OL,16,Farmed with a weapon before repeatedly
OL,17,Fstabbing the 24-year-old victim
OL,18,Fcausing serious injuries including a
OL,19,Fcollapsed lung.
