OL,6,FFollowing police searches of addresses
OL,7,Flinked to the suspect, evidence was
OL,8,Flocated linking Pirot to the crime,
OL,9,Fand he was arrested in December 2022
OL,10,Fon suspicion of grievous bodily harm
OL,11,Fwith intent.
OL,13,FHe was bailed with strict conditions
OL,14,Fpending further enquiries and forensic
OL,15,Ftesting.
OL,17,FThe 20-year-old was charged with
OL,18,Fgrievous bodily harm in June 2023 and
OL,19,Ffound guilty at Brighton Crown Court
OL,20,Fin June 2024.
