OL,3,CBarber jailed after attacking man with
OL,4,Cscissors
OL,6,FHe was sentenced in January 2025 at
OL,7,FLewes Crown Court to 5 years behind
OL,8,Fbars.
OL,10,FDetective Constable Jack Page from
OL,11,FSussex Police, said: "The injuries
OL,12,Fsustained were very serious, and the
OL,13,Foutcome could have been much worse had
OL,14,Ftreatment not been sought promptly.
OL,16,F"We are pleased with the outcome, and
OL,17,Fthat a man capable of such a violent
OL,18,Fassault has been removed from the
OL,19,Fcommunity, making it a safer place as
OL,20,Fa result."
